snippet.title: Woman Walks After 15 Years Of Crippling Back Pain
snippet.description:
Miracles In Natitingou, Benin
Only Heaven can record all of the glorious and supernatural things that are happening at the Osborn Ministry International Festival of Faith & Miracles in Natitingou, Benin. What an honor to be the carrier of God's liberating life to these beautiful people.

snippet.title: Eastern Liberia | Snake Woman Delivered
snippet.description: During our 2014 miracle evangelism event in Monrovia, Liberia, a teenager was delivered from demon possession. In her village she was known as "the snake girl" because the demon caused her slither along the ground like a snake. This is what the enemy of God wants to do to people! The GOOD NEWS of Jesus is POWERFUL! During the preaching of the Gospel, the demon left her. The people were crazy with joy when they saw this beautiful young woman walking upright and giving thanks to Jesus Christ!

snippet.title: Tumor Disappears | Bitung, Indonesia
snippet.description:
When this Muslim young woman came dared to attend the Festival of Faith and Miracles in, she never dreamed that her life would be transformed by the wonderful love and salvation of Jesus.

She came with a large thyroid tumor hidden by her religious head wrap.

When she believed on Jesus something happened that beyond what she thought possible. THE TUMOR DISAPPEARED. She came to the platform to show the people her miracle, look at her spontaneous expression of gratitude as she lunges at me in a bold embrace. How precious! 

These are moments that are etched in our memories and that equally launch us forward with the Good News of Jesus' love and mercy!

Partner with us in bringing salvation, healing and joy to those who are trapped in sin and futile religion.

Dr. LaDonna and Team

snippet.title: Heart Healed! -Togo
snippet.description: http://www.Osborn.org/ This beautiful woman receives her miracle from Jesus on the first day of the Osborn Ministries International Festival in Togo, Africa.  Watch as she demonstrates that she no longer lives in pain and sickness.  Jesus is showing himself alive to people in Tsévié, Togo  and her life will no longer be the same. Visit the Osborn Ministries website: www.OSBORN.com.

snippet.title: Running Man -Togo
snippet.description:
Osborn Ministries International Togo, Africa Festival, Dr. LaDonna Osborn  http://www.Osborn.org/

Day 1 of the Tsévié Festival of Faith and Miracles. 
Word about us is spreading throughout the town and surrounding villages that 
Jesus is healing people at "The Place of Trees."

Tonight when we arrive at the grounds thousands of people have already 
gathered. But the majority of the multitude arrives after dark. It's 
impossible to see the edge of the crowd with the sparce available 
lighting.

I teach the people from the Bible story of the blind beggar who cried 
out to Jesus with faith and received his sight. Over and over I 
emphasized to the people, "There is no god like our God!" Our God 
hears the cry of a blind man. Our God talks to beggars. Our God opens 
the eyes of the blind. Our God has all power. This God has sent me to 
you to tell you that He knows about you. He wants to come to you and 
deliver you from the power of the devil."

Faith begins to rise in the hearts of the people. Thousands of people 
respond to the message and ask Jesus to come into their lives. It is 
moving to see their eagerness to receive Jesus and His new life.

Then I pray for the sick. There are so many. But the power of the Lord 
is always present to heal. It is the confidence that I have in the 
power of Christ's love that gives me the courage to stand before these 
precious people and tell them that God wants to heal them.

After the prayer I tell the people to do what they could not do 
before. The multitude turns into a mass of movement as people begin 
stretching, bending and walking. Gradually the platform is being 
filled with people ready to give a testimony to their healing miracle.

Many who were crippled are now demonstrating their healing. They run, 
jump, rejoice and thank God for their miracle.

The people shout and clap and one after another, people give their 
testimony of Christ's healing power.
